1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo prije ovoga izlaganja, ispričat ću nešto što su ovih dana, priča među ovim klanjateljima trajnog euharistijskog klanjanja,

2
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] čini se da je to bilo u Trnovčici, ali evo nisam siguran tamo gdje je kapela trajnog euharistijskog klanjanja,

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] znači dvojica braće, tamo se noću adoriraju po dvojice ili po dvije osobe,

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] u onom najtežem vremenu, to je od tri do četiri, obično je to najteži termin da ne zasmješ.

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ovaj jedan stalno spava nekako, kljuca glavom.

6
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Veli mi ovaj, pa dobro šta si popio? Kaže Nesicu.

7
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne trebaš to, trebaš gloriju popit će već.

8
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mi ovaj prijatelj, dobro bi bilo to napraviti ovakvu neku reklamu, to bi bila reklama dobra i za kamo,

9
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] a i za ovaj nas koji provodimo vrime pred presvetim.

10
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro je o gloria, znači slava. Mi ćemo danas nešto govoriti o Marinoj slavi.

11
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam jako bio inspiriran u dogvoru sa bratom Krunom.

12
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pričate onome što je svet Ivan Pava u drugi dobro naslutio što se događa po blažnoj djevice Mariji.

13
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se kroz nju, kao što je ona novo srce za crkvu, novo srce nove crkve, tako je kroz nju Bog i nas oblikuje.

14
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam stavio naslov prema jednoj mise od svetu Ivana Pavla drugog.

15
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Marinoj srcu rađa se novi svijet ljubavi.

16
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čut ćemo to na temelju njegovih nekoliko citata.

17
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Može izlaganje biti malo duboko, ali nema veze i mi smo duboki, srce je duboko u nama.

18
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Razmišljat ćemo o svemu tome, a ovo bit će i snimljeno, pa onda može se uvijek okoristiti s tim.

19
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki su to vidici. Kaže Ivan Pavol drugi ovako.

20
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Marijinu bezgriješnom srcu crkva ponovno pronalazi svoj izvor.

21
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad malo razmislimo, zvuči jednostavno, ali zapravo jako duboko.

22
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu se otkriva jednostavno stvaranje, rađanje uvijek nove crkve.

23
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je bila rođena na duhove, ali kroz povijeste je posebno da se ona reanimira.

24
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na novo rađa, po duhu svetu, a rađa se po njegovoj zaručnici, po blažnoj djevici Marije.

25
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] A to onda vrijedi i za svakoga nas osobno.

26
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda to vrijedi za tvoju obitelj, pa onda vrijedi i za cijele društvene procese, za cijelo društvo.

27
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:32,080
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, koja je moć i uloga Marina? Zbog čega?

28
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:38,219
[SPEAKER_00] Sve zbog toga što je njoj predano cijelo čovječanstvo, skriža.

29
00:02:38,219 --> 00:02:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kao gospodar, gospodar, vladar, vladara, na križu.

30
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:47,520
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Ivan evanđelist Isusa predstavlja da je to njegov kraljevski tron.

31
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:52,080
[SPEAKER_00] On odatle kraljuje, skriža. Isus kaže, evo ti majke.

32
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] I to se odnosi na Ivana i na svakoga čovjeka u ovom svijetu.

33
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je poistovjećen sa Ivano.

34
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] Također veli Ivan Pavao drugi u enciklici Redemptoris Mater od kupiteljeva majka.

35
00:03:06,819 --> 00:03:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] U Mariji zapučnje novi svijet, u koji je Bog ušao da bi čovjek mogao ući u svijet ljubavi s Bogom.

36
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:23,560
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u Mariji je započeo novi svijet, u koji je Bog ušao da bi čovjek mogao ući u svijet ljubavi s Bogom.

37
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Također, duboka rečenica.

38
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] Isto veli u jednoj svojoj katehezi iz 1986.

39
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] U trenutku kada izgovara svoje neka mi bude, u Marijinu bezgrišnom srcu rađa se novi odnos između Boga i čovjeka.

40
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dobre, to su samo neke naznake, ali još ću ja kroz ova predavanja donositi neke njegove citate.

41
00:03:53,659 --> 00:04:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, Marija je otvorila čovječanstvu put ljubavi koji nikada ne prestaje, te u srcu crkve budi novi žar ljubavi.

42
00:04:04,539 --> 00:04:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo da neke obnove koje se događaju u povijesti crkve, neki sveci, uvijek su bili izrazito povezani s Marijom.

43
00:04:15,659 --> 00:04:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Marija je preko njih učinila svoje dijelo i zapravo oni su preko nje tako što su se njoj izručili, njoj predali.

44
00:04:23,019 --> 00:04:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] E sad valja o Mariji razmišljati kao o savršenoj osobi, savršenoj ženi.

45
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kada razmišljamo o srcu Isusovo, kažemo da je to vrhunac Bože ljubavi prema čovjeku.

46
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Bog je iskazao vrhunac svoje ljubavi u Isusovom milosrednom srcu, u probodenom srcu.

47
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] A Marijino srce je savršenstvo ljudske ljubavi prema Bogu, simbol savršene ljudske ljubavi prema Bogu.

48
00:04:55,300 --> 00:05:09,720
[SPEAKER_00] I zato se mi njoj izručujemo, zato joj se posvećujemo da bi nas preoblikovala u moralne ljude, u ljude koji žive u milosti i koji bi što savršene ljubili njezinog sina.

49
00:05:10,420 --> 00:05:16,660
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u središtu svake marijanske pobožnosti je ljubav prema Isusu Hristu, ljubav prema Bogu.

50
00:05:17,699 --> 00:05:23,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ova misla od sv. Ivana Pavla II. u Marijino srcu rađa se novi svijet ljubavi.

51
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:27,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ukazuje na duboku teološku, ali i psihološku perspektivu.

52
00:05:27,939 --> 00:05:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce nije samo simbol pobožnosti, nego ikona preobražene ljudske osobnosti, osjećajnosti, potpuno uslađene s Božijom ljubav.

53
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:49,959
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je nama model da mi takvi trebamo po njoj biti, kako bi smo bili što savršeni služitelji Božji.

54
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je to tako? Uskoro ćemo slaviti bezgrešnost začeće Marijino.

55
00:05:55,680 --> 00:06:01,399
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što se u njoj, u tom bezgrešnom začeću, odsijeva posebno Božije svjetlo.

56
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] I kada smo mi s njom, ujedini s njom, onda se u tom svjetlu bezgrešnosti lakše susrećemo s njezinim sinom, lakše susrećemo s Bogom.

57
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] Bez Marije je jednostavno kao da lutamo, kao djece bez majke, kao da smo pogubljeni.

58
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ima razloga zašto je presveto trojstvo odlučilo darovati nama blaženo Djevice Marije.

59
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:28,120
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja vjerujem da će neki od vas danas i tekako posvjedočiti svoje iskustvo,

60
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] a vjerujem da biste svi to mogli, jer imate to iskustvo, ne biste inače imali hrabrosti u javnosti moliti pred ljudima.

61
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:52,620
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, takvo srce koje nama Bog darovao, srce Marino, može rađati novi svijet, svijet ljubavi, novi svijet odnosa s Bogom.

62
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] Onako kako je Bog htio.

63
00:06:55,040 --> 00:07:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] E ne zaboravite da se Marija uspoređuje kao novozavjetni kovčeg saveza.

64
00:07:01,019 --> 00:07:09,959
[SPEAKER_00] U starom zavetu, kada se svijetimo, taj kovčeg saveza morao se nekako u središtu naroda biti.

65
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bila se raspoređena plemena izraelska na sjever, na jug, na zapad, na istog,

66
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] a kovčeg saveza poprili su u samom središtu i svi su sa nekim posebnim poštovanjem imali taj odnos prema tom kovčegu saveza.

67
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] I kad su dolazili pred njega moliti se gospodinu Bogu, uvijek su svaćali da je to privilegirano mjesto.

68
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] I taj kovčeg saveza, vjerujem da ste ga mogli vidjeti onako negdje nacrtanog,

69
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] gore na sebi imao dva kerubina koji spajaju krila.

70
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:49,939
[SPEAKER_00] I sad između ta dva kerubina bio je taj jedan poklopac koji se zvao Prijestolje Milosti Vrata.

71
00:07:49,939 --> 00:07:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] I zato odatle Mariji taj naziv Prijestolje posebne, dakle jahvine naklonjenosti onima koji su tu kod kovčega saveza.

72
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] Sad u kovčegu saveza nalaze dvije ploče saveza, deset zapovjedi, Aronov štab koji je procvjetao i mana kao ona hrana kroz pustinju koju je gospod Bog davao,

73
00:08:15,779 --> 00:08:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] da im bude uvijek znak i čudo što je gospodin činio kroz pustinju.

74
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] A sad zamislite, Marija u sebi nosi sve to, to je samo simbol onoga što će biti u Kristu.

75
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] I svećiništvo, i euharistija, i žrtva, i zakon, i novi zakon, to je izljev duha svetog na pedesetnicu.

76
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je Marija više nego taj kovčeg saveza.

77
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, ako su Izraelici trebali imati tako posebno poštovanje prema tome predmetu,

78
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] koliko mi tek trebamo imati poštovanje prema toj živoj osobi.

79
00:08:48,779 --> 00:08:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je dala ljudsku narav svome sinu.

80
00:08:54,159 --> 00:09:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je sada i naš zadatak da i mi se izručujemo njoj, poput Isusa.

81
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali malo ćemo se osvrnuti na nju kao na osobnost.

82
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:12,620
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce predstavlja unutarnje cijelokupno ozdravljenje svega čovjeka.

83
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] U njoj možemo biti kompletni, možemo biti integrirani.

84
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:22,799
[SPEAKER_00] Posobno naša afektivnost, sposobnost ljubiti, da ljubimo druge,

85
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sposobnost da prihvaćamo ljubav.

86
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi ne znaju ni Božiju ljubav prihvatiti ako nisu Mariji izručeni.

87
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] Često o Bogu maštaju nas kroz jedan krivi način.

88
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kao nekoj božanskoj energiji, kao nekoj božanskoj sili.

89
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ne uopće kao onome koja je osoba.

90
00:09:44,179 --> 00:09:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kada se Mariji predajemo po svećujima, ona nam priopćava pravu sliku Boga.

91
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:51,600
[SPEAKER_00] Najviše po svome sinu, po Isusu Hrista.

92
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce je simbol savršene ljudske ljubavi prema Bogu.

93
00:09:57,919 --> 00:10:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tko ulazi u njezino srce posvetom, danas ćemo učiniti čin posvete,

94
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:06,620
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi, možemo reći, u taj prostor sigurne ljubavi.

95
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] Srce je uvijek bio, dakle, simbol taj majčinske sigurnosti.

96
00:10:11,700 --> 00:10:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] U srcu Marijinu, u srcu majčinu djeca se nalaze.

97
00:10:17,139 --> 00:10:21,879
[SPEAKER_00] Kod Marije i simbol savršene ljudske zrelosti.

98
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ona kao osoba savršena je, usavršena u svemu.

99
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Na tu majčinsku sigurnost, sigurnost srca, prvi se oslonio Krist gospodin.

100
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:37,220
[SPEAKER_00] Predao se da bude u vlasništu srca te majke.

101
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Htjeli mi ili ne, bez obzira koliko naše majke nisu savršene,

102
00:10:42,059 --> 00:10:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] ipak smo mi njihovo vlasništvo.

103
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] U njima smo začeli, ona nas je formirala, majka nam daje svoj krv,

104
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] svoj kisik, svoj meso, tako isto i blažna djevica Marija.

105
00:10:51,820 --> 00:10:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] Morala je biti bezgrešna, da bi se Isus od nje mogao formirati svoje čovještvo.

106
00:10:57,639 --> 00:11:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ima nešto evo što se u svoremenoj znanosti tekako može primijeniti

107
00:11:01,299 --> 00:11:02,580
[SPEAKER_00] na blažnu djevicu Mariju.

108
00:11:02,580 --> 00:11:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kada se promatra što se događa djetetu,

109
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:09,419
[SPEAKER_00] koje kad se rodi i u prvoj godini dana,

110
00:11:09,419 --> 00:11:14,120
[SPEAKER_00] kada je na majčinu krilu, na majčinim grudima, majčinim prsima,

111
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,580
[SPEAKER_00] ili bolje rečeno na majčinom srcu,

112
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:19,600
[SPEAKER_00] postoje tri stvari koje su u djetetu.

113
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:23,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je sve sigurno.

114
00:11:23,259 --> 00:11:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, voljen sam ili ljubljen sam.

115
00:11:30,379 --> 00:11:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] I treće, sve će biti dobro.

116
00:11:32,539 --> 00:11:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi to sada idemo duhovno prenijeti,

117
00:11:37,639 --> 00:11:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] to znači kad se posvjetujemo blažnoj djevici Mariji

118
00:11:41,139 --> 00:11:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] i sebe i svoju obitelj i narod,

119
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:45,879
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira što se sve u svijetu događa,

120
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:48,580
[SPEAKER_00] možemo imati sigurno pouzdanje,

121
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:52,580
[SPEAKER_00] bit će sve sigurno, bit će sve dobro.

122
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,179
[SPEAKER_00] Voljeni smo od Boga.

123
00:11:54,179 --> 00:11:57,580
[SPEAKER_00] Trijumfirat će na koncu Božja ljubav, Božje milostrđe.

124
00:11:59,779 --> 00:12:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] I kad razmatramo našu ikonografiju,

125
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] najviše se prikazuje gospa s malinim djetotom Isusom,

126
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] kako ga drži na svome srcu.

127
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] To je to duhovno značenje što se s nama događa

128
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,620
[SPEAKER_00] kada smo posvjećeni srcu Mariji,

129
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:16,419
[SPEAKER_00] ona nas stavlja na svoje srce i u svoje srce.

130
00:12:16,419 --> 00:12:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] I imam osjećaj, tu je sve sigurno,

131
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] bit će sve dobro, voljeni smo.

132
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:24,919
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nemam potpuno spoznaju Boga da je ljubav,

133
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Marija će mi to priopćiti.

134
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] I moći ću biti njezni svjedok,

135
00:12:29,179 --> 00:12:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Božje ljubavi, očeve ljubavi,

136
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kristove ljubavi u ovome svijetu.

137
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:42,620
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da to, ta sigurnost što smo posvjećeni Mariji,

138
00:12:42,620 --> 00:12:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi od toga da Bog postoji.

139
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ta sigurnost njoj dolazi od Boga.

140
00:12:47,259 --> 00:12:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] To nam i treba.

141
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] Predani Mariji, majici,

142
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:53,600
[SPEAKER_00] imamo osjećaj sve u Božjim rukama,

143
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] sve je sigurno.

144
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo,

145
00:12:55,559 --> 00:12:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] pripadamo.

146
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo njezini

147
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] i mi smo Božji.

148
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Posebno po krštenju.

149
00:13:03,139 --> 00:13:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ušli smo u taj nadnaravni život

150
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,879
[SPEAKER_00] presvjetoga trojstva.

151
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zato i možemo po krštenju

152
00:13:08,519 --> 00:13:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] primati milosti.

153
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] I onda duboki mir.

154
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj mir koji je u njezinom srcu

155
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] i sigurnost da smo njoj predani.

156
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mir zapravo koji dolazi od Boga.

157
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:19,399
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono kad Isus kaže

158
00:13:19,399 --> 00:13:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] mir vam svoj ostavljam,

159
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] mir vam svoj dajem.

160
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] Bez obzira kakve su procesi nemira u svijetu,

161
00:13:25,899 --> 00:13:27,419
[SPEAKER_00] mi kao Mariji,

162
00:13:27,419 --> 00:13:29,240
[SPEAKER_00] vojska kao Mariji predani,

163
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,820
[SPEAKER_00] imamo taj duboki nutarnji osjećaj,

164
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:32,379
[SPEAKER_00] uvjerenje.

165
00:13:32,379 --> 00:13:34,759
[SPEAKER_00] Mir nam je taj svjedočanstvo.

166
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] Božija će biti zadnja,

167
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bog pobjeđuje.

168
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali majka ima posebno poslanje

169
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom svijetu.

170
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:44,899
[SPEAKER_00] E sad kako mi na sebe

171
00:13:44,899 --> 00:13:47,120
[SPEAKER_00] tu Marijinu savršenost možemo primjenjivati?

172
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:50,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je njezino srce savršen model

173
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,379
[SPEAKER_00] zrelosti, posebno one afektivne,

174
00:13:52,379 --> 00:13:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] a to je nama potrebno,

175
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce moramo promatrati

176
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] kao savršeno,

177
00:13:57,659 --> 00:13:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] integrirano.

178
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] Što to znači?

179
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,879
[SPEAKER_00] Razum, osjećaj, volja

180
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom jedinstvu.

181
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dok od nas često ima

182
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] dihotomije.

183
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Razum bi htio jedno,

184
00:14:07,659 --> 00:14:09,080
[SPEAKER_00] volja drugo,

185
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,080
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaj treće.

186
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce potpuno stabilno

187
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] nije vođeno nikakvim strahom,

188
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] nikakvom potrebom

189
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,600
[SPEAKER_00] za vlastitom samokontrolom,

190
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] nego slobodno vođeno od Boga.

191
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] Savršeno je empatično,

192
00:14:24,019 --> 00:14:24,700
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino srce.

193
00:14:24,700 --> 00:14:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećajno, suosjećajno,

194
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,299
[SPEAKER_00] do upotpunosti.

195
00:14:28,299 --> 00:14:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] To se najbolje vidi pod križem.

196
00:14:31,019 --> 00:14:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje nikoga ne osuđuje

197
00:14:33,659 --> 00:14:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] svi oni koji

198
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] razapenju Isusa

199
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] i koji još hule na njega,

200
00:14:37,759 --> 00:14:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] ako si sin Boži,

201
00:14:39,539 --> 00:14:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] si iđi iz križa i tako dalje.

202
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:44,100
[SPEAKER_00] Marija savršeno mirna.

203
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:48,600
[SPEAKER_00] Što je ono što je pod križem

204
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] nekako porazilo sve neprijatelje?

205
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] ta šutnja isusove kalvarije,

206
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] šutnja Marijina,

207
00:14:57,059 --> 00:14:58,899
[SPEAKER_00] Isus na križu živ,

208
00:14:58,899 --> 00:15:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] a govor njegovih svetih rana

209
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] po kojima se mi spašavamo,

210
00:15:03,299 --> 00:15:05,240
[SPEAKER_00] po kojima se odkupljujemo.

211
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:09,080
[SPEAKER_00] i Marijino srce trajeno otvoreno

212
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] transcedenciji Bogu.

213
00:15:10,539 --> 00:15:13,240
[SPEAKER_00] Svijeste da je stalno od Boga nošena

214
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] i stalno u suradnji s njom.

215
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je to na što smo i mi

216
00:15:16,659 --> 00:15:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] pozvani nju slijediti.

217
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] E kada se mi njoj posvećujemo,

218
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] ona sama preuzima ulogu

219
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] u nama odgajati ono što nije dobro,

220
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] a mi to često ne vidimo.

221
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, sveci nas uče da prva stvar

222
00:15:32,659 --> 00:15:36,879
[SPEAKER_00] s kojom se gospa u našem životu

223
00:15:36,879 --> 00:15:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] razračunava je robstvo grijeha.

224
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš biti Marijini

225
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] i živjeti u teškom grijehu.

226
00:15:43,519 --> 00:15:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] Neke manje nesavršene stuve ćemo imati,

227
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,919
[SPEAKER_00] ali u robstvu teškog grijeha

228
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne može.

229
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:51,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno, savjest nam vrišti.

230
00:15:51,799 --> 00:15:54,620
[SPEAKER_00] Dok, recimo, suvremeni čovjek

231
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:56,379
[SPEAKER_00] htio bi napraviti čak i neki

232
00:15:56,379 --> 00:15:57,899
[SPEAKER_00] teološki koncept

233
00:15:57,899 --> 00:15:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] da je sve prihvatljivo,

234
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog, i Božja ljubav,

235
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] a da možemo legalizirati

236
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] bilo koji oblik grijeha

237
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] kao neku vlastitu potrebu

238
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] ili potrebu ljudske ljubave.

239
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:07,879
[SPEAKER_00] Što da kako,

240
00:16:07,879 --> 00:16:09,899
[SPEAKER_00] u Marijinom kontekstu,

241
00:16:09,899 --> 00:16:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] u savršenstvu njezine osobe

242
00:16:11,259 --> 00:16:13,399
[SPEAKER_00] nemoguće da se i na nama odrazi.

243
00:16:13,399 --> 00:16:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Marija,

244
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] posvetom našom njoj,

245
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] ona se uvijek bori za ono,

246
00:16:18,919 --> 00:16:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] iskonsko,

247
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] da idemo sigurnim putom

248
00:16:20,799 --> 00:16:21,620
[SPEAKER_00] spasenja,

249
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] da ne budemo neki,

250
00:16:24,139 --> 00:16:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam nija,

251
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] filozofski, psihološki,

252
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] teološki čak fanatici.

253
00:16:28,179 --> 00:16:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] Može se sve,

254
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] mogu se svi grijesi

255
00:16:30,659 --> 00:16:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] i i dalje imam osjećat

256
00:16:32,259 --> 00:16:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] da me Bog ljubi.

257
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:33,620
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

258
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Gospa prvo priprema

259
00:16:35,759 --> 00:16:37,220
[SPEAKER_00] očišćenje srca.

260
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim dalje,

261
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:42,240
[SPEAKER_00] osposobljava na se zatrpljenje.

262
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] Trpljenje je onako

263
00:16:44,019 --> 00:16:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] mora u životu biti.

264
00:16:46,379 --> 00:16:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] da nam ne bi bilo frustrirajuće,

265
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:48,639
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bi počeli

266
00:16:48,639 --> 00:16:49,740
[SPEAKER_00] prigovarati Bogu

267
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili da ne bi počeli

268
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne daj Bože mrziti ljude

269
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] zato što trpimo nešto

270
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom svijetu.

271
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:56,299
[SPEAKER_00] Mi to trpljenje osmišljavamo,

272
00:16:56,299 --> 00:16:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] predajemo njoj,

273
00:16:57,299 --> 00:16:59,240
[SPEAKER_00] predajemo kao zadovoljstveno

274
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,120
[SPEAKER_00] za naše grijehe,

275
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] zadovoljstveno za toliko uvrede

276
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] na našene srcu,

277
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse u srcu njezinu.

278
00:17:03,899 --> 00:17:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] Marija to prijima.

279
00:17:05,220 --> 00:17:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] I tako i mi postajemo

280
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] su od kupitelji.

281
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je jedini od kupitelji,

282
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] a mi postajemo su od kupitelji.

283
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne preziremo sebe

284
00:17:14,279 --> 00:17:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] i svoj život.

285
00:17:14,980 --> 00:17:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] Također s Marijom

286
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] nadladavamo strah

287
00:17:20,859 --> 00:17:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] od odbačenosti.

288
00:17:22,059 --> 00:17:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan od najtežih strahova.

289
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nadladava se svješću

290
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ljubljen od Boga.

291
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,839
[SPEAKER_00] Gospa koja je tako divna

292
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek ti postvrđuje

293
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:35,819
[SPEAKER_00] da je netko nju tako formirao.

294
00:17:35,819 --> 00:17:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] Maximilian Kolbe

295
00:17:37,539 --> 00:17:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] kad govore o Marijinom

296
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] bezgrešnom začeću,

297
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] često to govori

298
00:17:41,059 --> 00:17:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] da je to sam duh sveti.

299
00:17:42,779 --> 00:17:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] On je to bezgrešno začeća

300
00:17:44,339 --> 00:17:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] i ona je da kako

301
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao njegov dar.

302
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] I kad smo njoj posvećeni,

303
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] mi participiramo

304
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] na to njezinom svjetlu

305
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] bezgrešnosti

306
00:17:54,220 --> 00:17:55,859
[SPEAKER_00] i to nas svjetlo stalno čisti.

307
00:17:55,859 --> 00:17:58,299
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nas Marija usavršava.

308
00:17:58,299 --> 00:17:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno,

309
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] grijeh nam se počne gaditi,

310
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] počne nam smetati,

311
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] sva ćemo da treba nestati

312
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] iz našega života.

313
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:06,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubljeni smo od Boga.

314
00:18:06,339 --> 00:18:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubljen si od Boga.

315
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] Onda rješavaš se te svake potrebe

316
00:18:12,299 --> 00:18:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] da kontroliraš sve stvari.

317
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš ti sve kontrolirati.

318
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ni ti je dobro sve kontrolirati.

319
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mora i u stvari biti

320
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:20,700
[SPEAKER_00] prepuštene Bogu

321
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,839
[SPEAKER_00] kako s povjerenjem.

322
00:18:21,839 --> 00:18:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ko je s Marijom,

323
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:25,660
[SPEAKER_00] u njemu raste

324
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:26,799
[SPEAKER_00] krepost povjerenja,

325
00:18:26,799 --> 00:18:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] krepost nade,

326
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,779
[SPEAKER_00] krepost spouzdanja.

327
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] ona je tako važna

328
00:18:30,259 --> 00:18:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] za naš svakodnevni život.

329
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo što će biti sutra,

330
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] što će za godinu,

331
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] za dvije, za pet,

332
00:18:34,819 --> 00:18:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] ali živimo li u zajedništu

333
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] s Marijom u nama,

334
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,339
[SPEAKER_00] raste to pouzdanje,

335
00:18:39,339 --> 00:18:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] imamo potpuno uvjerenje,

336
00:18:40,539 --> 00:18:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] bit će sve dobro.

337
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] Bog vodi ovaj svijet i sve ima svoju svrhu,

338
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] a ja želim biti oruđe u njezinim rukama.

339
00:18:53,359 --> 00:18:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Također imamo isto strah od nesposobnosti da nešto primimo.

340
00:18:57,539 --> 00:19:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] To primimo od Boga.

341
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam dovoljno vjere,

342
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] nemam dovoljno pouzda,

343
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] nemam dovoljno ljubavi.

344
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Gospod kao svoje dijete,

345
00:19:06,579 --> 00:19:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] ona te smiruje.

346
00:19:08,799 --> 00:19:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] daje ti taj dar vjere.

347
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,259
[SPEAKER_00] S vjerom se prima.

348
00:19:12,259 --> 00:19:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] S vjerom se živi.

349
00:19:13,819 --> 00:19:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u Marijinom srcu

350
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:22,700
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek biva sposoban prihvatiti Božju ljubav

351
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] i sve više spoznaje da je od Boga voljen.

352
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek je to tako važno.

353
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:31,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi upoznajmo po Mariji pravu sliku Boga.

354
00:19:31,359 --> 00:19:31,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

355
00:19:31,859 --> 00:19:34,680
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je ona toga Boga začela.

356
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pod njezinim srcem, u njezinom krilu.

357
00:19:37,259 --> 00:19:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] I ona jedina poznaje od ljudi

358
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] savršenu sliku Bože.

359
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Evo nekih par samo crtica.

360
00:19:44,059 --> 00:19:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Ivan u svojoj poslanici.

361
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je svjetlo

362
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] i tame u njemu nema nikakve.

363
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:52,839
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kada samo malo razmišljamo.

364
00:19:52,839 --> 00:19:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] Koje su to duboke stvari?

365
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] Također kaže Bog je ljubav.

366
00:19:57,500 --> 00:20:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je svjetlo i tame u njemu nema nikakve.

367
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se to tumači?

368
00:20:02,839 --> 00:20:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] Što više živimo u Bogu,

369
00:20:04,819 --> 00:20:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] to nas više njegovo svjetlo privlače.

370
00:20:07,259 --> 00:20:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] I pročišćava.

371
00:20:08,779 --> 00:20:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] I oslobađa od straha,

372
00:20:11,259 --> 00:20:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] od tame, od nevolja.

373
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogo ljudi svjedoči,

374
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] pa skoro bih rekao,

375
00:20:16,579 --> 00:20:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] jedno 70% od svih koji su

376
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] molitelji krunice,

377
00:20:20,079 --> 00:20:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako su bile u nekim težim,

378
00:20:22,079 --> 00:20:23,759
[SPEAKER_00] anksioznim, depresivnim stanjima,

379
00:20:23,759 --> 00:20:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] da su po krunice došli,

380
00:20:25,519 --> 00:20:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] kao u neku vrstu

381
00:20:26,539 --> 00:20:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] nutarnjeg prosvjetljenja.

382
00:20:28,579 --> 00:20:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da im se tamo podrom duše

383
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:31,160
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjetljivo.

384
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ne za jedan dan,

385
00:20:32,980 --> 00:20:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego kroz duži period molitve svete krunice.

386
00:20:36,019 --> 00:20:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Gospa rješava tih takvih

387
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] tamnih strana našega iskustva,

388
00:20:41,539 --> 00:20:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] našeg života u kojemu živimo.

389
00:20:43,519 --> 00:20:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] Marija imala na zemlji savršen život

390
00:20:47,059 --> 00:20:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] u svjetlu Božjem.

391
00:20:48,819 --> 00:20:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nam ona to svjetlo priopćava,

392
00:20:50,819 --> 00:20:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] jer zna koliko nam je potrebno.

393
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nam pomaže prihvatiti sebe

394
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] kao Božje stvorenje.

395
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže,

396
00:21:00,059 --> 00:21:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] ljubi bližnjeg svoga kao samog sebe.

397
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo ljubiti sami sebe.

398
00:21:05,259 --> 00:21:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to sebična ljubav,

399
00:21:07,579 --> 00:21:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] nego zato što si stvorenje Božje.

400
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti roditelj,

401
00:21:11,819 --> 00:21:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] zar bih htio da tvoj sin ili kći

402
00:21:14,339 --> 00:21:15,740
[SPEAKER_00] da se stalno nešto preziru,

403
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:16,660
[SPEAKER_00] da ne vole svoj život?

404
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, htio bih da budu sretni.

405
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da voli svoj život,

406
00:21:19,519 --> 00:21:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] da je sretan što postojiš,

407
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:22,200
[SPEAKER_00] što živi.

408
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko tek naš Bog,

409
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] Otac Nebeski,

410
00:21:25,279 --> 00:21:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] želi da budeš sretan što postojiš

411
00:21:27,079 --> 00:21:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] i što si pozvan u vječnost.

412
00:21:28,759 --> 00:21:31,839
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to nam se sve preko Marije priopćava.

413
00:21:31,839 --> 00:21:33,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, treba prihvatiti sebe,

414
00:21:33,339 --> 00:21:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] voljeti sebe kao stvorenje Božje.

415
00:21:36,079 --> 00:21:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to sebičnost,

416
00:21:37,519 --> 00:21:39,240
[SPEAKER_00] nije nikakva posesivnost,

417
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno reći da svome životu.

418
00:21:42,380 --> 00:21:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] Reći da Božjem dijelu stvaranja.

419
00:21:45,019 --> 00:21:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] Upoznajemo Božu ljubav posebno

420
00:21:48,619 --> 00:21:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] u Hristo.

421
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Božja riječ kaže

422
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] dostojan je zaklan je jaganjac.

423
00:21:54,119 --> 00:21:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] Malo kad razmišljam o tome

424
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] i što govore crkveni otci.

425
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kada je došao u nebo,

426
00:21:59,859 --> 00:22:03,480
[SPEAKER_00] On je učinio nas sve dostojnim

427
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] po svome tijelu.

428
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je uzeo tijelo

429
00:22:05,819 --> 00:22:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] od blažene djevice Marije.

430
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je za nas kao zaklan je jaganjac.

431
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] Sve nas je učinio dostojnim pred Otcem Nebeskim.

432
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] i tu je negdje ključna stvar

433
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] sebe prihvaćanja kršćanskoga.

434
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sebe prihvaćam

435
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] tek tada na zreo način

436
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] kada se prihvaćam u Hristu.

437
00:22:27,359 --> 00:22:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] On me učinio dostojnim.

438
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:31,359
[SPEAKER_00] On me oprao svojom svetom krvljem.

439
00:22:31,359 --> 00:22:33,279
[SPEAKER_00] U njegovo sam ime kršten.

440
00:22:33,279 --> 00:22:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Očevo sam vlašništvo.

441
00:22:35,519 --> 00:22:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] i dostojan sam njegovom krlju

442
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] stati pred Otcem.

443
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ne svojim dostojanstva

444
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] nego njegovom krlju.

445
00:22:42,319 --> 00:22:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] I koga onda ne bi volio.

446
00:22:44,099 --> 00:22:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to su te stvari

447
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] koje nam po Marijinom čoveštu

448
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje je dala čoveštu Isusu Hristu

449
00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi k nama.

450
00:22:50,559 --> 00:22:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Marija pod križem

451
00:22:57,519 --> 00:22:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] i srce koje oprašta.

452
00:22:59,039 --> 00:23:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je s Bogom

453
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] može oprostiti do kraja.

454
00:23:02,839 --> 00:23:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Poput Marije

455
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite.

456
00:23:06,119 --> 00:23:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] Majka pod križem

457
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,740
[SPEAKER_00] gleda svog nevinog sina

458
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jaganjca.

459
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:12,259
[SPEAKER_00] Savršeno oprašta svima.

460
00:23:12,259 --> 00:23:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svim progoniteljima,

461
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] svim učiteljima,

462
00:23:14,819 --> 00:23:15,759
[SPEAKER_00] svim mrziteljima.

463
00:23:15,759 --> 00:23:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] I tako do posljednjega

464
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] čoveka na ovoj zemlji.

465
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oprost proizlazi

466
00:23:21,799 --> 00:23:22,839
[SPEAKER_00] iz jedinstva

467
00:23:22,839 --> 00:23:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] s Isusovim srcem.

468
00:23:24,319 --> 00:23:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ako netko kaže

469
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu oprostiti.

470
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si kršćanin, lažeš.

471
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Isus kaže

472
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] ako vi ne oprostite

473
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] ni vama otac neće oprostiti.

474
00:23:34,519 --> 00:23:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ne bi to rekao

475
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] da mi to ne možemo.

476
00:23:36,980 --> 00:23:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] Jer što znači

477
00:23:38,819 --> 00:23:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] na kršćanski način oprostiti?

478
00:23:40,299 --> 00:23:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajmo Isusa na križu

479
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] i On kaže

480
00:23:43,099 --> 00:23:44,839
[SPEAKER_00] Oče, oprostim,

481
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:46,160
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaju što čine.

482
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:48,640
[SPEAKER_00] Oni i ne traže oprostiti,

483
00:23:48,640 --> 00:23:50,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali Isus sveći unaprijed oprašta.

484
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kada mi opraštamo,

485
00:23:53,859 --> 00:23:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] mi opraštamo u ime toga

486
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] Isusova dijela na križu.

487
00:23:57,359 --> 00:24:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je prvi svima sve oprostio.

488
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] I ti kao krštenik,

489
00:24:02,339 --> 00:24:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] kao njegovo tijelo,

490
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] možeš oprostiti u ime njegovog dijela,

491
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] u ime Isusovo ja opraštam.

492
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] To znači u ime onog njegovog dijela na križu.

493
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zato svi koji se bave ovom

494
00:24:11,819 --> 00:24:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] problematikom

495
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] oprostiti, neoprostiti,

496
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] kažu

497
00:24:15,819 --> 00:24:17,839
[SPEAKER_00] Oprostiti se mora,

498
00:24:17,839 --> 00:24:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne moraš uopće emocionalno tako osjećati.

499
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš čak ni osjećati potrebu da oprostiš.

500
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ili posebno ne može to biti popraćeno

501
00:24:24,480 --> 00:24:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] baš tvojim emocijama.

502
00:24:26,099 --> 00:24:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti napravi odluku oprostiti.

503
00:24:29,079 --> 00:24:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] Opraštam osobi,

504
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] to i to je.

505
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,259
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i nekoj osobi,

506
00:24:33,259 --> 00:24:34,839
[SPEAKER_00] ako gledaš na televiziji,

507
00:24:34,839 --> 00:24:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] pa je netko napravo neko zlo,

508
00:24:36,039 --> 00:24:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja mu Isuse opraštam u tvoje ime.

509
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] Olaksavaš sebi.

510
00:24:40,759 --> 00:24:41,779
[SPEAKER_00] A kamo li onima

511
00:24:41,779 --> 00:24:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji su te konkretno povrijedili u životu?

512
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ima jedna šaljiva

513
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:47,660
[SPEAKER_00] monaška izreka

514
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] zašto Isus kad govori

515
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] da opraštamo svojim bližnjima

516
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] tu zapovjed povezu

517
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] i sa oni i sa neprijateljima.

518
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže zato što

519
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] neretko stoji jedne te iste osobe.

520
00:24:59,619 --> 00:25:01,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, naši najbližnji

521
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] mogu nam nekad biti

522
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] i najveći neprijatelji.

523
00:25:03,339 --> 00:25:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] Što ne mora ništa biti čudno,

524
00:25:05,759 --> 00:25:06,660
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno

525
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:08,660
[SPEAKER_00] to je svakodnevno testiranje

526
00:25:08,660 --> 00:25:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] opraštaš li

527
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne opraštaš.

528
00:25:10,619 --> 00:25:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono kad Isus kaže Petru

529
00:25:12,019 --> 00:25:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] ne sedam puta,

530
00:25:13,619 --> 00:25:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] nego do sedamdeset puta,

531
00:25:15,099 --> 00:25:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] sedam.

532
00:25:15,559 --> 00:25:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači onaj koji marin,

533
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] on mora moći opraštati.

534
00:25:19,599 --> 00:25:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kada opraštamo,

535
00:25:21,119 --> 00:25:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] otpuštamo,

536
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] mi jednostavno izbacujemo

537
00:25:24,079 --> 00:25:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] otrov iz svoga srca,

538
00:25:26,220 --> 00:25:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali i otrovi iz našega društva.

539
00:25:29,339 --> 00:25:31,259
[SPEAKER_00] djavao bih htio da ne opraštamo,

540
00:25:31,259 --> 00:25:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] da se nekako mrzimo,

541
00:25:33,619 --> 00:25:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] da pravdamo,

542
00:25:34,519 --> 00:25:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] da progonimo druge

543
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji su ne pobrijedili.

544
00:25:36,619 --> 00:25:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kada mi opraštamo,

545
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] Bog po tome tvome činu vjere,

546
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer je opraštanje čin vjere,

547
00:25:43,099 --> 00:25:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] posebno kada prihvaćaš samo

548
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,839
[SPEAKER_00] zdravo razumski,

549
00:25:46,839 --> 00:25:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, još nemaš u sebi osjećaja oprostiti.

550
00:25:49,519 --> 00:25:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] ti činiš čin vjere.

551
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] Po tome činu vjere,

552
00:25:52,579 --> 00:25:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] upravo što je bila veća uvreda u tebi,

553
00:25:54,759 --> 00:25:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] možemo tako reći,

554
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] veća rupa bila.

555
00:25:57,039 --> 00:25:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sada ispunjavati Bog tu rupu

556
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] svojom vodom opraštanja,

557
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,799
[SPEAKER_00] svojim milosređem,

558
00:26:03,799 --> 00:26:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] svojom ljubavi.

559
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dobivaš veći dar ljubavi.

560
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Po svetom bezgrišnom srcu Marijinu

561
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] naša se preobrazba događa

562
00:26:14,180 --> 00:26:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] po duhu svetom,

563
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] njezinom božanskom zaručnikom.

564
00:26:19,519 --> 00:26:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naša se osobnost razvija

565
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] prema zrelosti ljubavi

566
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] i prema samopredanju.

567
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] Što je čovjek više u ljubavi,

568
00:26:26,859 --> 00:26:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] svima potrebe više se darivati.

569
00:26:29,140 --> 00:26:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] Takav je Bog po sebi.

570
00:26:31,099 --> 00:26:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna od definicija Boga je

571
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] sebedarje, sebedarivanje.

572
00:26:35,259 --> 00:26:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] To se savršeno vidi u Isu Hristo,

573
00:26:37,539 --> 00:26:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] u duhu svetom.

574
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] Istinska ljubav čovjeka usavršuje

575
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] i oslobađa ga da bude ono što jest.

576
00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš biti ono što jest,

577
00:26:48,619 --> 00:26:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] što Bog s tobom žele u svijetu,

578
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] sve dok nisi ušao u tu božoj ljubav.

579
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:54,319
[SPEAKER_00] Trebaš se davati.

580
00:26:54,319 --> 00:26:55,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bog poziva sve da se daju,

581
00:26:55,900 --> 00:26:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] da se žrtvuju,

582
00:26:56,619 --> 00:26:58,759
[SPEAKER_00] da budu predani ovom svijetu

583
00:26:58,759 --> 00:27:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] iz ljubavi i nikog ne osuđuju.

584
00:27:00,940 --> 00:27:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ignacijanski, gledano prema modelu

585
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] svetog Ignacija,

586
00:27:05,980 --> 00:27:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnim vježbama,

587
00:27:08,079 --> 00:27:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] to je proces uređenja

588
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] našeg afektivnog svijeta

589
00:27:12,079 --> 00:27:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] kroz obraćenje,

590
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] on to naziva neuredne

591
00:27:14,039 --> 00:27:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili neki to zovu

592
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] neuređene sklonosti,

593
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] prema unutranjem skladu,

594
00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] prema duhovnoj slobodi.

595
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] Znam što je sa mnom upravljalo,

596
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:24,200
[SPEAKER_00] što je diktiralo.

597
00:27:25,059 --> 00:27:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Posvećujem se Mariji sve više i više,

598
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] čisti se moje srce,

599
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] živim u milosti,

600
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] sve više bivan slobodan

601
00:27:30,819 --> 00:27:32,359
[SPEAKER_00] od svih procesa u ovom svijetu

602
00:27:32,359 --> 00:27:33,200
[SPEAKER_00] koji me zarobljava

603
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] i posebno od osobnih grijeha,

604
00:27:35,099 --> 00:27:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] možda kojima sam prije robovao.

605
00:27:37,140 --> 00:27:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam puno od braća svećenika

606
00:27:41,019 --> 00:27:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji kažu da

607
00:27:41,819 --> 00:27:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad se posvećiš ti blažnoj djevici,

608
00:27:45,059 --> 00:27:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mariji, dobro,

609
00:27:45,599 --> 00:27:47,339
[SPEAKER_00] neke stvari brzo nestanu iz života,

610
00:27:47,339 --> 00:27:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] ali neke stvari kroz duži proces,

611
00:27:49,819 --> 00:27:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] možda uređenje tvoga karaktera.

612
00:27:52,019 --> 00:27:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi smo ih nikada izbalansirali

613
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] uredili da se nismo predavali Mariji,

614
00:27:56,759 --> 00:27:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] da se nismo njoj posvećivali.

615
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] Zato će gospod kod dongo obja reći

616
00:28:01,319 --> 00:28:03,160
[SPEAKER_00] posvećujte se ako možete

617
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] i svaki dan

618
00:28:04,339 --> 00:28:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] mome bezgrišnom srcu.

619
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Marijin osjećani život

620
00:28:14,039 --> 00:28:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] nije potisnut,

621
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego je potpuno prožete

622
00:28:17,940 --> 00:28:18,859
[SPEAKER_00] duhom svetim.

623
00:28:18,859 --> 00:28:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] Eto zašto i mi

624
00:28:20,579 --> 00:28:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] svoja afektivna stanja

625
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] moramo s njom prolaziti

626
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] i predavati njoj

627
00:28:26,019 --> 00:28:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se integrirala

628
00:28:27,519 --> 00:28:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] Božjo milošću

629
00:28:28,519 --> 00:28:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tu posvetu.

630
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:31,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nama se nekad

631
00:28:31,339 --> 00:28:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] neke emocije pojave

632
00:28:32,519 --> 00:28:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ne znamo uvijek zašto.

633
00:28:34,599 --> 00:28:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nekad stremaje prema grihu,

634
00:28:36,599 --> 00:28:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] nekad nas zbunjuju.

635
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] Trebamo ih predavati Mariji,

636
00:28:39,759 --> 00:28:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] srcu Mariji.

637
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ona će ih predati Isusu.

638
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] I milošće ih Božja

639
00:28:44,019 --> 00:28:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] integrirati,

640
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] osmisliti će ih.

641
00:28:45,819 --> 00:28:47,200
[SPEAKER_00] U suprotnom,

642
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] možemo nekad jednostavno

643
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] se zatvoriti,

644
00:28:49,519 --> 00:28:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] gurnuti emocije pod tepih

645
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] i mogu negdje u kasnim godinama

646
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] opet na jedan

647
00:28:55,299 --> 00:28:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] skroz subtilan i nenormalan način

648
00:28:59,119 --> 00:29:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] eksplodirati.

649
00:29:03,799 --> 00:29:05,640
[SPEAKER_00] Marija se radoje u punini.

650
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, savršeno se radoje.

651
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Prožeta je vedrinom i ljubavljom.

652
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] Plače kao i svaka osoba.

653
00:29:11,819 --> 00:29:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] Trpi i ljubi.

654
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bez zatvaranja u sebe.

655
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek ostaje otvorena

656
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] za primanje

657
00:29:19,079 --> 00:29:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] i oblikovanje čovjeka

658
00:29:21,039 --> 00:29:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] i novoga čovječanstva.

659
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što je Bog njoj dao pod križe.

660
00:29:24,900 --> 00:29:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je takva.

661
00:29:26,099 --> 00:29:27,160
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli život bila

662
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] savršena osobnost

663
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] i u punini je dobila

664
00:29:31,019 --> 00:29:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] svojim uznesenjem

665
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] i sada to na nas prenosi

666
00:29:33,599 --> 00:29:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] kada se mi njoj posvećujemo.

667
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže ovako gospa

668
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:38,660
[SPEAKER_00] kod Don Gobija.

669
00:29:38,660 --> 00:29:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo da je ta plava knjiga

670
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] od crkve odobrena

671
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,839
[SPEAKER_00] i ja ću vam danas svima podijeliti

672
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] po jedan primjerak.

673
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] Uđite u moje bezgrešno srce.

674
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je kolijevka

675
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] u koju želim položiti

676
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] svu svoju djecu.

677
00:29:54,579 --> 00:29:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje vam pomažem,

678
00:29:57,279 --> 00:29:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] dakle u njezinom bezgrešnom srcu,

679
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] da položite staroga čovjeka

680
00:30:01,799 --> 00:30:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] grijeha i zla,

681
00:30:02,799 --> 00:30:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] sebičnosti i oholosti,

682
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] zlobe i nečistoće,

683
00:30:06,819 --> 00:30:09,359
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje ja oblikujem u vama

684
00:30:09,359 --> 00:30:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] novog čovjeka.

685
00:30:10,980 --> 00:30:12,839
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite ta misa

686
00:30:12,839 --> 00:30:13,779
[SPEAKER_00] od Ivana Pavla II.

687
00:30:13,779 --> 00:30:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da u Marijinom srcu

688
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] nastaje novi čovjek.

689
00:30:16,819 --> 00:30:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo kako to gospa

690
00:30:18,460 --> 00:30:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje istu stvar govori.

691
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje ja, dakle u svom srcu,

692
00:30:21,579 --> 00:30:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] u vama oblikujem

693
00:30:22,619 --> 00:30:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] novog čovjeka,

694
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] čovjeka milosti i dobrote,

695
00:30:25,799 --> 00:30:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] čovjeka ljubavi i poniznosti,

696
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] čovjeka, svetosti i čistoće.

697
00:30:30,619 --> 00:30:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] Sada ćemo se mi sabrati,

698
00:30:33,819 --> 00:30:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću to podijeliti u dva dijela

699
00:30:35,259 --> 00:30:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovo predavanje,

700
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] sada ćemo se sabrati,

701
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] izmolit ćemo jednu deseticu hrunice,

702
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda ću drugi dio

703
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] nešto još izložiti.

704
00:30:41,319 --> 00:30:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ćemo gledati da to buduje

705
00:30:43,279 --> 00:30:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] na što kontemplativni način.

706
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] To znači zatvorit ćemo oče.

707
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:51,279
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislit ćemo Mariju,

708
00:30:51,279 --> 00:30:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] možda u klečećem stavu,

709
00:30:52,819 --> 00:30:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono kada

710
00:30:53,460 --> 00:30:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Andžio Gabriel

711
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi k njoj.

712
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo kako nas potiču sveci,

713
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] posebno oni koji su nas

714
00:31:01,019 --> 00:31:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] uvodili u kontemplaciju,

715
00:31:03,039 --> 00:31:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] da mi zamislimo Mariju

716
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:06,660
[SPEAKER_00] kako izgledala.

717
00:31:06,759 --> 00:31:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Najprije vidimo ambijentone sobe.

718
00:31:08,519 --> 00:31:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] To je neka sobica Nazarecka

719
00:31:11,180 --> 00:31:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] u toj njezinoj kućici.

720
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno je bila neka soba

721
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] posebna za molitvo.

722
00:31:16,799 --> 00:31:19,720
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ćeš promotriti te zidove

723
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:20,640
[SPEAKER_00] da su od kamena,

724
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,839
[SPEAKER_00] kako već moglo biti.

725
00:31:21,839 --> 00:31:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ćeš promotriti

726
00:31:24,099 --> 00:31:26,160
[SPEAKER_00] da je Marija na nekom klecalu

727
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] skloptjenih ruku.

728
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ćeš primijetiti

729
00:31:30,859 --> 00:31:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] kako izgleda na njoj haljina.

730
00:31:33,759 --> 00:31:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ćeš primijetiti

731
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] njeno ozareno lice.

732
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ono što je važno

733
00:31:41,539 --> 00:31:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] shvati da je ona bezgrešna.

734
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sva je prožeta

735
00:31:47,299 --> 00:31:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] nad naravnim svjetlom

736
00:31:48,539 --> 00:31:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] Duha Svetoga.

737
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] I ti na neki način

738
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] već sada

739
00:31:53,420 --> 00:31:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] uđi u to svjetlo njezina srca,

740
00:31:56,839 --> 00:31:58,160
[SPEAKER_00] uđi u njezino srce.

741
00:31:58,160 --> 00:32:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ona te želi primiti

742
00:32:00,519 --> 00:32:02,740
[SPEAKER_00] u svoje srce.

743
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] kao što će sada

744
00:32:06,859 --> 00:32:08,799
[SPEAKER_00] primiti Isusa

745
00:32:08,799 --> 00:32:10,259
[SPEAKER_00] pod svoje srce,

746
00:32:10,259 --> 00:32:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] u svoju utrobu.

747
00:32:11,099 --> 00:32:14,660
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je tako odredio

748
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] da njegov sin

749
00:32:16,900 --> 00:32:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] bude pod srcem Marine,

750
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] da bude

751
00:32:19,579 --> 00:32:20,160
[SPEAKER_00] oblikovan

752
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:21,700
[SPEAKER_00] pod njezino srcem.

753
00:32:22,539 --> 00:32:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] zato želi da i mi tako

754
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] budemo od nje formirani

755
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] u drugoga Krista.

756
00:32:28,019 --> 00:32:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] Oče naš

757
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:32,640
[SPEAKER_00] koji jesi na nebesima,

758
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] sveti se

759
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] ime Tvoje,

760
00:32:35,099 --> 00:32:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] dođi

761
00:32:36,319 --> 00:32:37,660
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevstvo Tvoje,

762
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] budi volja Tvoja,

763
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] kako na nebu,

764
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:42,759
[SPEAKER_00] tako i na zemlji.

